snippet.title: Twin Mirror - Paris Games Week Gameplay Trailer | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
Peer deeper into the life of Sam Higgs, his alter ego, and his mind palace in this new Twin Mirror gameplay trailer from Paris Games Week. 

Stay tuned for more info on Twin Mirror which will launch in 2019.
